<F P=102>   LD3004153894 Stockholm Radio Sweden in Swedish 1445 GMT 30 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3004153894 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>
<F P=105>  Swedish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] There was a small fire today at the Oskarshamn 
nuclear power plant when a cable in the turbine house of Reactor 
3 caught fire. The actual reactor was not affected by the fire, 
which has now been extinguished. The management of the nuclear 
power plant expects that Reactor 3 will return to full capacity 
later today. 

</TEXT>

