<H3> <TI>   Report Urges Fund for Decommissioning Reactors </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Report Urges Fund for Decommissioning Reactors </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0305140694 London FINANCIAL TIMES in English 3 May 94 p 
9--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM0305140694 </F>
<F P=104>  London FINANCIAL TIMES </F>
