  [Text] (ANSA) Rome, May 3 -- Italy's premier-designate 
Silvio Berlusconi had a half-hour informal meeting this evening 
with Japan's new premier Tsutomu Hata, at the request of the 
latter, "to say hello and get to know each other," Berlusconi's 
spokesman said. 
