the importance he places on the July Naples G-7 summit -- the 
reason why he chose Italy to start a European tour which will 
take him to Paris (tomorrow), Bonn and Brussels. 
  Separately, the premier-designate had talks with Italy's 
Ambassador to the United States Boris Banchieri on U.S. 
President Bill Clinton's June 2-3 visit to Italy. 

