<H3> <TI>   Japanese Prime Minister Hata Begins Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Japanese Prime Minister Hata Begins Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Discusses G-7, Russian Aid With Ciampi </H4>

<F P=102> BR0405075694 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1425 GMT 3 
May 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR0405075694 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
