<H3> <TI>   FRY Refuses To Readmit Deported Kosovo Albanians </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    FRY Refuses To Readmit Deported Kosovo Albanians </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0305180394 Stockholm Radio Sweden in English 1615 GMT 3 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0305180394 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Two bus-loads of Kosovo Albanian asylum-seekers 
deported from Sweden have been stopped by authorities at the 
Serbian border. It's the third time deported Kosovo Albanians 
from Sweden have been refused entry into Serbia in the last few 
weeks. Swedish authorities say Belgrade is violating human 
rights by refusing its own citizens entry into the country. 

</TEXT>

