<F P=102>   LD0305215294 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1800 GMT 
3 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0305215294 </F>
<F P=104>  Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
